OL,3,CFour-legged heroes: Police unveil
OL,4,Cmemorial bench to honour fallen police
OL,5,Cdogs
OL,7,FCumbria Constabulary has unveiled a
OL,8,Fmemorial bench installed to honour the
OL,9,Fservice and dedication of police dogs.
OL,11,FThe bench, located at the Cumbria
OL,12,FPolice Dog Section at Police HQ in
OL,13,FPenrith, has an engraved plaque which
OL,14,Freads: "In memory of all the police
OL,15,Fdogs that have served the people of
OL,16,FCumbria."
OL,18,FThe police service says it "recognises
OL,19,Fthe bravery, loyalty and commitment
OL,20,Fshown by these animals throughout
OL,21,Ftheir service".
