OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1779639072
OL,3,CFour-legged heroes: Police unveil
OL,4,Cmemorial bench to honour fallen police
OL,5,Cdogs
OL,7,FSergeant Martin Mould said: "Police
OL,8,Fdogs are far more than operational
OL,9,Fassets - they are trusted partners who
OL,10,Fput themselves in harm's way to
OL,11,Fprotect both officers and the public.
OL,13,F"This bench is a fitting tribute to
OL,14,Fthe incredible contribution they have
OL,15,Fmade over the years, and it gives us
OL,16,Fall a place to reflect on their
OL,17,Fservice and sacrifice."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
