OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1779639072
OL,3,CFour-legged heroes: Police unveil
OL,4,Cmemorial bench to honour fallen police
OL,5,Cdogs
OL,7,FHere are some of Cumbria's retired
OL,8,Fpolice dogs - or RPDs. They are all
OL,9,Fstill alive, and are enjoying their
OL,10,Ffree time now that they have been
OL,11,Ftaken off the beat.
OL,13,FCumbria's Police, Fire and Crime
OL,14,FCommissioner, David Allen, said: "Our
OL,15,Fpolice dogs play a vital role in
OL,16,Fpolicing to keep the public safe and
OL,17,Fstop criminals in their tracks.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
