PN,35604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1779639072
OL,3,CFour-legged heroes: Police unveil
OL,4,Cmemorial bench to honour fallen police
OL,5,Cdogs
OL,7,F"They are incredibly valued and loved
OL,8,Fwithin the Constabulary so I'm pleased
OL,9,Fto see them being recognised and
OL,10,Fhonoured for their service."
OL,12,FPaul Caine, from Little and Caine, who
OL,13,Fdonated the bench, added: "We are
OL,14,Fincredibly proud to donate this bench
OL,15,Fin recognition of the police dogs who
OL,16,Fhave served Cumbria.
OL,18,F"Their dedication and bravery often go
OL,19,Funseen, but their impact on
OL,20,Fcommunities is huge.
