OL,3,CFour-legged heroes: Police unveil
OL,4,Cmemorial bench to honour fallen police
OL,5,Cdogs
OL,7,F"We hope this memorial helps highlight
OL,8,Ftheir important role and gives people
OL,9,Fa moment to remember them."
